data.description: This home is in the coveted Three Creeks Community with an entry that opens up to a large living room with high vaulted ceilings. There is a large eat-in kitchen that opens to the backyard with a custom built bar giving ample space for indoor/outdoor entertaining. There are French Doors that lead to a large primary bedroom on the main floor with a ensuite bathroom that has a double vanity as well as a separate tub and shower. There is a half bath on the main floor so that your guests don't need to use yours and the laundry room is also downstairs for easy access. The upstairs has two nice sized secondary bedrooms and a bathroom, as well as a huge loft that can be used as a game room, media room or you can close it in to create a fourth bedroom. There is new carpet throughout that was installed in Oct. of 22 and new paint in the kitchen and secondary bedrooms upstairs.
